line_1: Since drums and parchment were invented.
line_2: And well revenge may rest contented,

line_1: "Nay, more, the hellish monster has invented,
line_2: "(Had not my care the deep-laid plot prevented)

line_1: Each day grinning Envy additions invented;
line_2: A thousand kind females the story augmented —
For who is pleas'd, if not tormented?
